  <description>
    <p>
      MuseAmp (Music + Amplifier) is an audio level normalizer/amplifier that makes your audio files play at the same normalized level.
      It can either directly alter your audio files to amplify their native volume or simply apply a ReplayGain 2.0 standard tag to your files so your audio player of choice knows what audio level to play the audio at.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Supports .mp3 and .flac files</li>
      <li>ReplayGain 2.0 tagging and direct gain adjustment</li>
      <li>Batch processing and folder support</li>
      <li>Modern PySide6 (Qt) interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
